manufacturerProductDescription.media_text: Elevate your communication with Stationery Paper & Self-Adhesive Envelopes Set Crafted with precision, DUGUTUL set includes 30 sheets of charming writing paper and 18 matching envelopes. Whether it's a heartfelt thank-you note, a motivational message, or an important announcement, our stationery is your canvas for expressing emotions.

Designed for both printer and handwriting compatibility, our stationery ensures seamless versatility. The collection of 6 unique stationery and envelope cover designs adds a touch of warmth and sophistication, making each correspondence more memorable.

High quality letter writing is smooth High quality invitation Each stationary paper sheet is 100 gsm, is compatible with both inkjet and laser printers; Perfect for use with ballpoint pens, gel pens, fountain pens, pencils, etc.The paper material of stationery set is durable and thick enough, so don't worry the ink will bleed the paper.

Compatible with inkjet and laser printer Decoration Paper This stationery set is perfect for scrapbook crafting, invitations, certificates, poetry scrolls, calligraphy, documents, letters, short stories, illustrating, poems, lyrics, letters to Santa and much more. Suitable for adults, children, and students. You will like to using this stationery set to personalize your arts & crafts and impress others.

Impressive Envelope The envelope that complements the paper highlights your heartwarm and gives the recipient a greater feeling. The envelope comes with glue, making it very convenient to seal, saving you time, energy, and money.

Multifaceted Utility Ideal for penpals, business invitations, parties, and creative expression, our set suits various occasions. Timeless Elegance The collection of 6 captivating designs enhances your messages, conveying sentiments with style. Uncompromising Quality Smooth and high-quality paper ensures that every word is expressed beautifully. Thoughtful Presentation Thoughtfully designed adhesive envelopes add elegance to sealing, saving you time and making your messages more memorable. Product Features Stationery Paper Size: 10.2 x 7.3 inches / 26 x 18.5 cm Envelope Size: 8.6 x 4.3 inches / 22 x 11 cm Package Contents 30 x Charming Stationery Sheets 18 x Coordinating Envelopes
